261
00:12:57,000 --> 00:13:00,440
Listen to me, when they come, we’ll behave accordingly.

262
00:13:00,520 --> 00:13:03,520
I promise you, don’t worry. Okay?
-Yeah, I promise too.

263
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:06,800
Wait, where are the men?
-In the mourning room. They’re gluing PVC.

264
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:10,680
On Shabbat? Working on Shabbat?

265
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:14,440
Soon you’ll have a barbecue
in the middle of the living room with pigs,

266
00:13:14,560 --> 00:13:17,280
