-Chips are kosher.

267
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:20,760
From potatoes that didn’t have
tithes taken from them on Shabbat of the sabbatical year?

268
00:13:21,160 --> 00:13:24,200
What?
-How much impurity in one house?

269
00:13:25,040 --> 00:13:25,960
Yuck.

270
00:13:28,040 --> 00:13:30,480
Thank God she didn’t convert.
-Let them call.

271
00:13:34,760 --> 00:13:36,800
I don’t know what smells worse, the glue

272
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:40,320
