-How did glue get on my shirt? I don’t get it.

273
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:44,200
What’s this mess, for heaven’s sake?

274
00:13:44,680 --> 00:13:46,840
Why mess? We’re gluing a carpet.
-And Moshe?

275
00:13:46,920 --> 00:13:51,120
He’s gluing shoes, socks, and clothes.
He’s going for avant-garde art.

276
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:53,440
Helping them a bit.
-I see.

277
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:56,160
Well, you’re not leaving the room under any circumstances,

278
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:59,960
