282
00:14:13,040 --> 00:14:14,920
Clear?
-So when can we leave?

283
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:17,160
When I release you.
-When? After Shabbat?

284
00:14:17,640 --> 00:14:22,240
Yes, you’ll be the three stars.
The moment you leave the room,

285
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:27,840
for me, Shabbat is over,
it’ll only be spontaneous

286
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:30,440
according to my instructions. Clear?
-Yeah.

287
00:14:31,000 --> 00:14:31,920
Yeah.
-Of course. Of course.

288
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:34,840
I think he’s here, behind the fridge.

289
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:37,360
Girls, I don’t want to join Mirav’s game.

290
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:39,320
I recommend you not tell her anything about this,

291
00:14:39,800 --> 00:14:41,840
take Manny and the kids
and scram before the religious folks come.

292
00:14:41,920 --> 00:14:43,520
On the other hand, she won’t stay for the parts that are going to be

293
00:14:43,680 --> 00:14:45,160
for sure.
-Of course.

294
00:14:45,240 --> 00:14:47,960
Yeah, but I...
-Forget it for now, close the laundry in the kitchen.

295
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:50,720
We have to catch them.
Close off this whole area,

296
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:52,200
so he doesn’t escape to that side.
-Yeah.

297
00:14:52,280 --> 00:14:55,680
I’m stressing them out here, by the fridge.
Wherever he goes, you catch him.

298
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:56,880
Focus.

299
00:14:59,800 --> 00:15:00,640
Here he is!
-Here.

300
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:01,560
Here.

301
00:15:03,520 --> 00:15:04,640
Now he ran away.

302
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:07,600
Alin, sit down, Orna, in my room.
I'll get you skirts.

303
00:15:07,680 --> 00:15:10,360
But Meirav, the hamster.
-I don't care about your hamster.

304
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:12,200
