305
00:15:12,840 --> 00:15:15,840
Tell me, Meirav, can we not be so uptight?

306
00:15:15,920 --> 00:15:19,600
It's not uptight. It's just a little bit of pretending, that's all.

307
00:15:20,160 --> 00:15:23,040
Meirav, I really don't want
to wear those skirts...

308
00:15:23,120 --> 00:15:25,360
Sit down..
-Yeah, I don't really want to either.

309
00:15:25,680 --> 00:15:27,400
