the shiksa in every Jewish family.

311
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:32,600
We don't have interfaith marriages in our family!

312
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:35,520
Ugh, but I'm scared
that Manny will see me... religious,

313
00:15:35,640 --> 00:15:36,960
