-Oh, funny, Mom.

327
00:16:14,880 --> 00:16:16,520
I can't believe it. God willing.

328
00:16:17,280 --> 00:16:19,000
Where's Orna?
-Here’s Orna. Orna.

329
00:16:19,160 --> 00:16:21,320
She just... Meirav says she's too pretty,

330
00:16:21,400 --> 00:16:22,960
