431
00:22:07,440 --> 00:22:10,280
Pigs! Shrimp in milk with potatoes.

432
00:22:11,920 --> 00:22:13,040
Gross.

433
00:22:14,120 --> 00:22:15,240
That's the cousin of the PVC.

434
00:22:20,240 --> 00:22:22,720
This wireless babaji along with Justin Beaton.

435
00:22:23,240 --> 00:22:24,360
Beaton?

436
00:22:24,440 --> 00:22:26,920
Which Beaton?
-Bieber, Bieber.

437
00:22:29,280 --> 00:22:30,320
Where did you get that from?

438
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:33,200
Well, we need to paddle around.

439
00:22:35,240 --> 00:22:36,960
Sorry. No, because of that...

440
00:22:37,520 --> 00:22:40,240
I suggest you don't go in there
because it smells really bad like garbage.

441
00:22:45,040 --> 00:22:46,040
Do you want something to drink?

442
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:53,840
He didn't tell you to do...

443
00:22:55,480 --> 00:22:56,320
No.

